dcterms:description: A multiplayer variant of Tic-Tac-Toe, dubbed 'Tic-Tac-Mo', which adds an additional player and expands the board size to 3x5 while maintaining the 3-in-a-row win condition.
dcterms:title: Tic-Tac-Mo

dcterms:creator: Joseph Antonius Maria Nijssen
dcterms:description: A multiplayer variant of Connect 4, dubbed 'Connect 3x3', which adds an additional player and changes the win condition to 3-in-a-row while keeping the board size at 6x7.
dcterms:title: Connect 3x3
